title: Tom Spacington Rogue 1.2.2
description:
New android space action game
Similar to old Rogue game
Levels, items and enemies are randomly generated
Try to get as far as you can without dying

Version 1.2.2 - current version as of 27th Nov 2012
Over 100 items - all stats are random
3 playable ships each with 3 sub-types
Random quests on planets

What's new in 1.2.2?
Second boss ship added
AI improved
